title: David Dobrik
itunes:title: David Dobrik
itunes:subtitle: David Dobrik is a YouTube star, voice actor and entertainer. He and Anna talk about David’s rise to fame, his dislike of pets, dating, friendship, and elaborate pranks. David and Anna then give some Unqualified advice to Amy.
